</manufacturer>
</person>
 movie <it><link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../867/390867.xml">
UHF</link></it>, which had to be significantly rewritten. The film was dedicated to his memory. Silva is interred at the <cemetery wordnetid="108521623" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
